{"tid":16042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俏老師寄猥褻照　教室內課輔口愛","createTime":"2016-12-01T09:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T12:42:55.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"288573fdd5077bcd49daf57e03b56c0fa892d1ea","tid":16042,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T09:29:59.000Z","msg":"美國康乃狄克州一名39歲英文女老師馬琪絲(Allison Marchese)，在丹尼爾韓德高中(Daniel Hand High School)任職期間，涉嫌對2名男學生寄猥褻照、傳情色簡訊，甚至在教室內對其中一名學生進行「口交課輔」。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《鏡報》報導，馬琪絲從前年開始看上兩名學生，其中一名才年僅14歲。馬琪絲先是約他們出來吃午餐，然後說：「你們長得好帥，害我上課沒辦法專心。」然後學生回應「請老師自重」，但馬琪絲卻說「你讓我好傷心，你背叛了我」。另外一名現年17歲的男學生說，馬琪絲不斷傳給他色情簡訊和猥褻照，兩人甚至在一間教室內進行口交，但該名學生也承認，曾經要利用這段醜聞，計畫向馬琪絲勒索200美金(約新台幣6000元)。<br />\n<br />\n目前馬琪絲被控犯下第2級性騷擾罪與性危害，最高恐被判20年徒刑，預計全案將在明年3月宣判。<br />\n<br />\n台灣網友則認為：「我怎麼遇不到這種老師呢？」、「不用衝著我來嗎？」、「老師只是上健康教育操作課程。」、「要是我有個這麼善解人意的老實，我的青春就不會如此悶悶不樂了。」（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"cadd5283355bd7783d74204ebe1666d0eb1fff62","tid":16042,"uid":2192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T09:30:32.000Z","msg":"41j"},{"pid":"073dab294f6695a9861df1a6b83b36fa5ca75145","tid":16042,"uid":35248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:43:30.000Z","msg":"施"},{"pid":"e6e5db485f0a5cbc2b6176c8c106c9e04f31352a","tid":16042,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:46:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又加一分"},{"pid":"99b6f7ecf09e2acc06f19db67a561d774a6e4d8e","tid":16042,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:48:32.000Z","msg":"快點"},{"pid":"3db6f13a528016d902e9dc751591d0884258f4c2","tid":16042,"uid":23763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:55:10.000Z","msg":"Hello 冇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00adf71b17d235603d1855958db8d99e4339144","tid":16042,"uid":2961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:41:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/01/204057_713d9d6055763f6dffbd73baec7d4361.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F01%2F204057_713d9d6055763f6dffbd73baec7d4361.jpg&h=6d54678c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c802877590ff3a2df6d34075d575b94d402eb4","tid":16042,"uid":26672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:42:55.000Z","msg":"MILF<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當我有講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}